OL,3,CNetwork Rail warns people are 'risking
OL,4,Cit all' at level crossings
OL,6,FNetwork Rail has warned that people
OL,7,Fare 'risking it all' when using level
OL,8,Fcrossings on the railway network.
OL,10,FThe company, which is responsible for
OL,11,Fmaintaining tracks and infrastructure,
OL,12,Fsays there have been more than 1500
OL,13,Fincidents in the past four years.
OL,15,FIt says distractions, such as mobile
OL,16,Fphone usage, is driving a rise in near
OL,17,Fmiss incidents, which are up by 16%.
OL,19,FIt is urging people to be careful when
OL,20,Fon the railway, and to be fully alert
OL,21,Fwhen using crossings.
