OL,3,CNetwork Rail warns people are 'risking
OL,4,Cit all' at level crossings
OL,6,FThe release of the footage comes as
OL,7,Fnew research commissioned by Network
OL,8,FRail shows that 47% of people in the
OL,9,FSouth East admit they have made a
OL,10,Fmistake whilst being distracted by
OL,11,Ftheir phone.
OL,13,FWatch: CCTV released by Network Rail
OL,14,Fshows a number of near misses on the
OL,15,Frailway network.
OL,17,FThe data also shows that young people
OL,18,Fare among the most distracted, with
OL,19,F87% of Gen Z and 70% of Millennials
OL,20,Fadmitting to mistakes.
