OL,3,CNetwork Rail warns people are 'risking
OL,4,Cit all' at level crossings
OL,6,F"I wasn't being deliberately reckless
OL,7,For rushing, but perhaps because I used
OL,8,Fthe station every day and knew it so
OL,9,Fwell, I'd become a bit complacent.
OL,11,F"I went with everyone else without
OL,12,Fstopping to think for myself.
OL,13,FRemember, no appointment or
OL,14,Fdestination is worth risking your life
OL,15,Ffor.
OL,17,F"Always look carefully and never
OL,18,Fassume it's safe to cross. It's better
OL,19,Fto be late in this world, than early
OL,20,Fin the next."
